//   Fresh C2:
//     193.233.202.17  : 44729   (SOCKS proxy for svchost32.exe)
//     77.110.122.137  : 37182   (alt SOCKS proxy)
//     45.86.230.112            (pre-ransomware staging)
//     Cloudflare WARP tunnels from non-IT endpoints
